dct_title_s: Sanborn Map of Highland Park, New Jersey - Map 45
dct_description_sm: This is map 45 in the Sanborn series of maps of Highland Park, circa 1919-1929 (exact date unknown). The map shows the area bounded by River Road, Raritan, Rutgers Place, and Lawrence, with portions of Harrison, Adelaide, Grant, Parkway, Lincoln, and the Raritan River with a bridge from Raritan Ave.
From the Rutgers University Special Collections/University Archives uncatalogued collection.
Purpose: To map the city of Highland Park for insurance purposes.
